[ENG]
TDD with Mock Objects: Design Principles and Emerging Properties

Here you can find:
- the last draft of the paper
- the questionnaire aimed to access the relationship between the practice in use of TDD and the adherence to SOLID principles
- the code of TDD micro-exercises


If you are interested to participate to this experiment:
1) answer the short questionnaire
2) implementation your solution of the TDD micro-exercises and send your code
3) receive one solution of the TDD micro-exercises developed with the practices described in the paper


To send the code or for any comments and questions you can contact me from:
- http://github.com/lucaminudel
- http://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaminudel
- http://twitter.com/lukadotnet
- http://blogs.ugidotnet.org/luKa/contact.aspx




[ITA]
TDD with Mock Objects: Design Principles and Emerging Properties

Qui puoi trovare:
- l'ultima bozza del paper
- il questionario che ha l'obiettivo di verificare la relazione tra la pratica in uso del TDD e la aderenza ai principi SOLID
- il codice dei micro-esercizi in TDD


Per partecipare a questo esperimento:
1) rispondi al breve questionario
2) scrivi la tua soluzione dei micro-esercizi in TDD e invia il codice
3) ricevi una soluzione dei micro-esercizi in TDD sviluppata secondo le pratiche descritte nel paper


Per inviare il codice o per qualunque commento o domanda puoi contattarmi qui:
- http://github.com/lucaminudel
- http://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaminudel
- http://twitter.com/lukadotnet
- http://blogs.ugidotnet.org/luKa/contact.aspx
